    "One plausible explanation is that pivoting each loss term relative to the abnormal detection loss enhances the model's sensitivity to anomalies, thereby improving its ability to capture sequential patterns in transactions.In conclusion, the multipurpose foundation model TREASURE is more efficient and effective than multiple single-purpose models.",
    "Furthermore, the adopted loss aggregation strategy is substantially more effective than the alternative baseline strategies.",
    "Overall, TREASURE demonstrates a significant RI, outperforming the currently deployed system by 111%.",
